  "title": "⚡⚡️ ENTRY-LEVEL SALES EXECUTIVE ⚡️",
  "description": "<p>Training Provided | High Commission | Uncapped Earnings | Career Progression</p><p>💡 LOOKING TO START A SALES CAREER WITH BIG INCOME?</p><p>This role is perfect if you want to:</p><p>Build valuable sales and communication skills</p><p>Earn performance-based commissions with no cap</p><p>Grow fast with clear career progression</p><p>Work with a supportive team that pushes you to succeed</p><p>👤 WHO SHOULD APPLY?</p><p>Fresh graduates seeking a fast-paced, rewarding role</p><p>ORD personnel ready to take charge of their career</p><p>Career switchers wanting a fresh start with growth potential</p><p>Anyone with a positive attitude and willingness to learn</p><p>No experience? No problem! We provide full training.</p><p>🎯 YOUR RESPONSIBILITIES</p><p>Connect and build rapport with potential customers</p><p>Understand customer needs and recommend appropriate solutions</p><p>Present products clearly and confidently</p><p>Manage objections and close sales professionally</p><p>Collaborate with your team to achieve targets</p><p>📚 TRAINING & DEVELOPMENT</p><p>Comprehensive onboarding and ongoing coaching</p><p>Practical sales techniques and product knowledge</p><p>Daily mentorship from experienced leaders</p><p>Regular feedback and support to improve performance</p><p>We help you grow both professionally and personally.</p><p>💸 EARNINGS & REWARDS</p><p>Competitive, performance-based commission scheme</p><p>Unlimited earning potential — the harder you work, the more you earn</p><p>Incentives, bonuses, and travel rewards for top performers</p><p>🚀 CAREER PATHWAY</p><p>Sales Executive</p><p>Senior Sales Executive</p><p>Team Leader</p><p>Sales Manager</p><p>Your growth is based on results and leadership ability.</p><p>🌟 TEAM CULTURE</p><p>Friendly, motivated, and supportive environment</p><p>Team bonding activities and social nights</p><p>Recognition programs to celebrate achievements</p><p>Leaders dedicated to mentoring and coaching</p><p>🚫 THIS ROLE MAY NOT BE FOR YOU IF</p><p>You prefer fixed pay with no pressure</p><p>You dislike performance-driven roles</p><p>You avoid responsibility or challenges</p><p>👉 READY TO START?</p><p>🔥 DM “EXEC” or apply now!</p><p>🔥 Limited training slots available</p><p>Make your first sales job your stepping stone to success.</p>",
